390        $objWriter->writeAttribute('xlink:actuate', 'onLoad');

392        $objWriter->endElement();
393

395            // office:event-listeners
396            $objWriter->startElement('office:event-listeners');
397            // presentation:event-listener
398            $objWriter->startElement('presentation:event-listener');

403            $objWriter->writeAttribute('xlink:show', 'embed');
404            $objWriter->writeAttribute('xlink:actuate', 'onRequest');
405            // > presentation:event-listener
406            $objWriter->endElement();
407            // > office:event-listeners
408            $objWriter->endElement();
409        }
410
411        $objWriter->endElement();

414    /**
415     * Write text.
416     *
417     * @throws \Exception
418     */
419    public function writeShapeTxt(XMLWriter $objWriter, RichText $shape): void
420    {
421        // draw:frame
422        $objWriter->startElement('draw:frame');
423        $objWriter->writeAttribute('draw:style-name', 'gr' . $this->shapeId);
424        $objWriter->writeAttribute('svg:width', Text::numberFormat(CommonDrawing::pixelsToCentimeters($shape->getWidth()), 3) . 'cm');
425        $objWriter->writeAttribute('svg:height', Text::numberFormat(CommonDrawing::pixelsToCentimeters($shape->getHeight()), 3) . 'cm');
426        $objWriter->writeAttribute('svg:x', Text::numberFormat(CommonDrawing::pixelsToCentimeters($shape->getOffsetX()), 3) . 'cm');
427        $objWriter->writeAttribute('svg:y', Text::numberFormat(CommonDrawing::pixelsToCentimeters($shape->getOffsetY()), 3) . 'cm');
428        // draw:text-box
429        $objWriter->startElement('draw:text-box');
430
431        $paragraphs = $shape->getParagraphs();
432        $paragraphId = 0;
433        $sCstShpLastBullet = '';
434        $iCstShpLastBulletLvl = 0;
435        $bCstShpHasBullet = false;
436
437        foreach ($paragraphs as $paragraph) {
438            // Close the bullet list
439            if ('bullet' != $sCstShpLastBullet && true === $bCstShpHasBullet) {
440                for ($iInc = $iCstShpLastBulletLvl; $iInc >= 0; --$iInc) {
441                    // text:list-item
442                    $objWriter->endElement();
443                    // text:list
444                    $objWriter->endElement();
445                }
446            }
447            //===============================================
448            // Paragraph
449            //===============================================
450            if ('none' == $paragraph->getBulletStyle()->getBulletType()) {
451                ++$paragraphId;
452                // text:p
453                $objWriter->startElement('text:p');
454                $objWriter->writeAttribute('text:style-name', 'P_' . $paragraph->getHashCode());
455
456                // Loop trough rich text elements
457                $richtexts = $paragraph->getRichTextElements();
458                $richtextId = 0;
459                foreach ($richtexts as $richtext) {
460                    ++$richtextId;
461                    if ($richtext instanceof TextElement) {
462                        // text:span
463                        $objWriter->startElement('text:span');
464                        if ($richtext instanceof Run) {
465                            $objWriter->writeAttribute('text:style-name', 'T_' . $richtext->getHashCode());
466                        }
467                        if (true === $richtext->hasHyperlink() && '' != $richtext->getHyperlink()->getUrl()) {
468                            // text:a
469                            $objWriter->startElement('text:a');
470                            $objWriter->writeAttribute('xlink:type', 'simple');
471                            $objWriter->writeAttribute('xlink:href', $richtext->getHyperlink()->getUrl());
472                            $objWriter->text($richtext->getText());
473                            $objWriter->endElement();
474                        } else {
475                            $objWriter->text($richtext->getText());
476                        }
477                        $objWriter->endElement();
478                    } elseif ($richtext instanceof BreakElement) {
479                        // text:span
480                        $objWriter->startElement('text:span');
481                        // text:line-break
482                        $objWriter->startElement('text:line-break');
483                        $objWriter->endElement();
484                        $objWriter->endElement();
485                    }
486                }
487                $objWriter->endElement();
488            //===============================================
489            // Bullet list
490            //===============================================
491            } elseif ('bullet' == $paragraph->getBulletStyle()->getBulletType()) {
492                $bCstShpHasBullet = true;
493                // Open the bullet list
494                if ('bullet' != $sCstShpLastBullet || ($sCstShpLastBullet == $paragraph->getBulletStyle()->getBulletType() && $iCstShpLastBulletLvl < $paragraph->getAlignment()->getLevel())) {
495                    // text:list
496                    $objWriter->startElement('text:list');
497                    $objWriter->writeAttribute('text:style-name', 'L_' . $paragraph->getBulletStyle()->getHashCode());
498                }
499                if ('bullet' == $sCstShpLastBullet) {
500                    if ($iCstShpLastBulletLvl == $paragraph->getAlignment()->getLevel()) {
501                        // text:list-item
502                        $objWriter->endElement();
503                    } elseif ($iCstShpLastBulletLvl > $paragraph->getAlignment()->getLevel()) {
504                        // text:list-item
505                        $objWriter->endElement();
506                        // text:list
507                        $objWriter->endElement();
508                        // text:list-item
509                        $objWriter->endElement();
510                    }
511                }
512
513                // text:list-item
514                $objWriter->startElement('text:list-item');
515                ++$paragraphId;
516                // text:p
517                $objWriter->startElement('text:p');
518                $objWriter->writeAttribute('text:style-name', 'P_' . $paragraph->getHashCode());
519
520                // Loop trough rich text elements
521                $richtexts = $paragraph->getRichTextElements();
522                $richtextId = 0;
523                foreach ($richtexts as $richtext) {
524                    ++$richtextId;
525                    if ($richtext instanceof TextElement) {
526                        // text:span
527                        $objWriter->startElement('text:span');
528                        if ($richtext instanceof Run) {
529                            $objWriter->writeAttribute('text:style-name', 'T_' . $richtext->getHashCode());
530                        }
531                        if (true === $richtext->hasHyperlink() && '' != $richtext->getHyperlink()->getUrl()) {
532                            // text:a
533                            $objWriter->startElement('text:a');
534                            $objWriter->writeAttribute('xlink:type', 'simple');
535                            $objWriter->writeAttribute('xlink:href', $richtext->getHyperlink()->getUrl());
536                            $objWriter->text($richtext->getText());
537                            $objWriter->endElement();
538                        } else {
539                            $objWriter->text($richtext->getText());
540                        }
541                        $objWriter->endElement();
542                    } elseif ($richtext instanceof BreakElement) {
543                        // text:span
544                        $objWriter->startElement('text:span');
545                        // text:line-break
546                        $objWriter->startElement('text:line-break');
547                        $objWriter->endElement();
548                        $objWriter->endElement();
549                    }
550                }
551                $objWriter->endElement();
552            }
553            $sCstShpLastBullet = $paragraph->getBulletStyle()->getBulletType();
554            $iCstShpLastBulletLvl = $paragraph->getAlignment()->getLevel();
555        }
556
557        // Close the bullet list
558        if ('bullet' == $sCstShpLastBullet && true === $bCstShpHasBullet) {
559            for ($iInc = $iCstShpLastBulletLvl; $iInc >= 0; --$iInc) {
560                // text:list-item
561                $objWriter->endElement();
562                // text:list
563                $objWriter->endElement();
564            }
565        }
566
567        // > draw:text-box
568        $objWriter->endElement();
569        // > draw:frame
570        $objWriter->endElement();
571    }

612    /**
613     * Write table Shape.
614     *
615     * @throws \Exception
616     */
617    public function writeShapeTable(XMLWriter $objWriter, Table $shape): void
618    {
619        // draw:frame
620        $objWriter->startElement('draw:frame');
621        $objWriter->writeAttribute('svg:x', Text::numberFormat(CommonDrawing::pixelsToCentimeters($shape->getOffsetX()), 3) . 'cm');
622        $objWriter->writeAttribute('svg:y', Text::numberFormat(CommonDrawing::pixelsToCentimeters($shape->getOffsetY()), 3) . 'cm');
623        $objWriter->writeAttribute('svg:height', Text::numberFormat(CommonDrawing::pixelsToCentimeters($shape->getHeight()), 3) . 'cm');
624        $objWriter->writeAttribute('svg:width', Text::numberFormat(CommonDrawing::pixelsToCentimeters($shape->getWidth()), 3) . 'cm');
625
626        $arrayRows = $shape->getRows();
627        if (!empty($arrayRows)) {
628            $firstRow = reset($arrayRows);
629            $arrayCells = $firstRow->getCells();
630            // table:table
631            $objWriter->startElement('table:table');
632            foreach ($arrayCells as $shapeCell) {
633                $objWriter->startElement('table:table-column');
634                $objWriter->endElement();
635            }
636            foreach ($arrayRows as $keyRow => $shapeRow) {
637                // table:table-row
638                $objWriter->startElement('table:table-row');
639                $objWriter->writeAttribute('table:style-name', 'gr' . $this->shapeId . 'r' . $keyRow);
640                //@todo getFill
641
642                $numColspan = 0;
643                foreach ($shapeRow->getCells() as $keyCell => $shapeCell) {
644                    if (0 == $numColspan) {
645                        // table:table-cell
646                        $objWriter->startElement('table:table-cell');
647                        $objWriter->writeAttribute('table:style-name', 'gr' . $this->shapeId . 'r' . $keyRow . 'c' . $keyCell);
648                        if ($shapeCell->getColspan() > 1) {
649                            $objWriter->writeAttribute('table:number-columns-spanned', $shapeCell->getColspan());
650                            $numColspan = $shapeCell->getColspan() - 1;
651                        }
652
653                        // text:p
654                        $objWriter->startElement('text:p');
655
656                        // text:span
657                        foreach ($shapeCell->getParagraphs() as $shapeParagraph) {
658                            foreach ($shapeParagraph->getRichTextElements() as $shapeRichText) {
659                                if ($shapeRichText instanceof TextElement) {
660                                    // text:span
661                                    $objWriter->startElement('text:span');
662                                    if ($shapeRichText instanceof Run) {
663                                        $objWriter->writeAttribute('text:style-name', 'T_' . $shapeRichText->getHashCode());
664                                    }
665                                    if (true === $shapeRichText->hasHyperlink() && '' !== $shapeRichText->getHyperlink()->getUrl()) {
666                                        // text:a
667                                        $objWriter->startElement('text:a');
668                                        $objWriter->writeAttribute('xlink:type', 'simple');
669                                        $objWriter->writeAttribute('xlink:href', $shapeRichText->getHyperlink()->getUrl());
670                                        $objWriter->text($shapeRichText->getText());
671                                        $objWriter->endElement();
672                                    } else {
673                                        $objWriter->text($shapeRichText->getText());
674                                    }
675                                    $objWriter->endElement();
676                                } elseif ($shapeRichText instanceof BreakElement) {
677                                    // text:span
678                                    $objWriter->startElement('text:span');
679                                    // text:line-break
680                                    $objWriter->startElement('text:line-break');
681                                    $objWriter->endElement();
682                                    $objWriter->endElement();
683                                }
684                            }
685                        }
686
687                        // > text:p
688                        $objWriter->endElement();
689
690                        // > table:table-cell
691                        $objWriter->endElement();
692                    } else {
693                        // table:covered-table-cell
694                        $objWriter->writeElement('table:covered-table-cell');
695                        --$numColspan;
696                    }
697                }
698                // > table:table-row
699                $objWriter->endElement();
700            }
701            // > table:table
702            $objWriter->endElement();
703        }
704        // > draw:frame
705        $objWriter->endElement();
706    }

740     * Writes a group of shapes.
741     *
742     * @throws \Exception
743     */
744    public function writeShapeGroup(XMLWriter $objWriter, Group $group): void
745    {
746        // draw:g
747        $objWriter->startElement('draw:g');
748
749        $shapes = $group->getShapeCollection();
750        foreach ($shapes as $shape) {
751            // Increment $this->shapeId
752            ++$this->shapeId;
753
754            // Check type
755            if ($shape instanceof RichText) {
756                $this->writeShapeTxt($objWriter, $shape);
757            } elseif ($shape instanceof Table) {
758                $this->writeShapeTable($objWriter, $shape);
759            } elseif ($shape instanceof Line) {
760                $this->writeShapeLine($objWriter, $shape);
761            } elseif ($shape instanceof Chart) {
762                $this->writeShapeChart($objWriter, $shape);
763            } elseif ($shape instanceof AbstractDrawingAdapter) {
764                $this->writeShapeDrawing($objWriter, $shape);
765            } elseif ($shape instanceof Group) {
766                $this->writeShapeGroup($objWriter, $shape);
767            }
768        }
769
770        $objWriter->endElement(); // draw:g
771    }

799    /**
800     * Write the default style information for a RichText shape.
801     */
802    public function writeTxtStyle(XMLWriter $objWriter, RichText $shape): void
803    {
804        // style:style
805        $objWriter->startElement('style:style');
806        $objWriter->writeAttribute('style:name', 'gr' . $this->shapeId);
807        $objWriter->writeAttribute('style:family', 'graphic');
808        $objWriter->writeAttribute('style:parent-style-name', 'standard');
809        // style:graphic-properties
810        $objWriter->startElement('style:graphic-properties');
811        $objWriter->writeAttribute('style:mirror', 'none');
812        $this->writeStylePartShadow($objWriter, $shape->getShadow());
813        if (is_bool($shape->hasAutoShrinkVertical())) {
814            $objWriter->writeAttribute('draw:auto-grow-height', var_export($shape->hasAutoShrinkVertical(), true));
815        }
816        if (is_bool($shape->hasAutoShrinkHorizontal())) {
817            $objWriter->writeAttribute('draw:auto-grow-width', var_export($shape->hasAutoShrinkHorizontal(), true));
818        }
819        // Fill
820        switch ($shape->getFill()->getFillType()) {
821            case Fill::FILL_GRADIENT_LINEAR:
822            case Fill::FILL_GRADIENT_PATH:
823                $objWriter->writeAttribute('draw:fill', 'gradient');
824                $objWriter->writeAttribute('draw:fill-gradient-name', 'gradient_' . $shape->getFill()->getHashCode());
825                break;
826            case Fill::FILL_SOLID:
827                $objWriter->writeAttribute('draw:fill', 'solid');
828                $objWriter->writeAttribute('draw:fill-color', '#' . $shape->getFill()->getStartColor()->getRGB());
829                break;
830            case Fill::FILL_NONE:
831            default:
832                $objWriter->writeAttribute('draw:fill', 'none');
833                $objWriter->writeAttribute('draw:fill-color', '#' . $shape->getFill()->getStartColor()->getRGB());
834                break;
835        }
836        // Border
837        if (Border::LINE_NONE == $shape->getBorder()->getLineStyle()) {
838            $objWriter->writeAttribute('draw:stroke', 'none');
839        } else {
840            $objWriter->writeAttribute('svg:stroke-color', '#' . $shape->getBorder()->getColor()->getRGB());
841            $objWriter->writeAttribute('svg:stroke-width', number_format(CommonDrawing::pointsToCentimeters($shape->getBorder()->getLineWidth()), 3, '.', '') . 'cm');
842            switch ($shape->getBorder()->getDashStyle()) {
843                case Border::DASH_SOLID:
844                    $objWriter->writeAttribute('draw:stroke', 'solid');
845                    break;
846                case Border::DASH_DASH:
847                case Border::DASH_DASHDOT:
848                case Border::DASH_DOT:
849                case Border::DASH_LARGEDASH:
850                case Border::DASH_LARGEDASHDOT:
851                case Border::DASH_LARGEDASHDOTDOT:
852                case Border::DASH_SYSDASH:
853                case Border::DASH_SYSDASHDOT:
854                case Border::DASH_SYSDASHDOTDOT:
855                case Border::DASH_SYSDOT:
856                    $objWriter->writeAttribute('draw:stroke', 'dash');
857                    $objWriter->writeAttribute('draw:stroke-dash', 'strokeDash_' . $shape->getBorder()->getDashStyle());
858                    break;
859                default:
860                    $objWriter->writeAttribute('draw:stroke', 'none');
861                    break;
862            }
863        }
864
865        $objWriter->writeAttribute('fo:wrap-option', 'wrap');
866        // > style:graphic-properties
867        $objWriter->endElement();
868        // > style:style
869        $objWriter->endElement();
870
871        $paragraphs = $shape->getParagraphs();
872        $paragraphId = 0;
873        foreach ($paragraphs as $paragraph) {
874            ++$paragraphId;
875
876            // Style des paragraphes
877            if (!isset($this->arrStyleParagraph[$paragraph->getHashCode()])) {
878                $this->arrStyleParagraph[$paragraph->getHashCode()] = $paragraph;
879            }
880
881            // Style des listes
882            $bulletStyleHashCode = $paragraph->getBulletStyle()->getHashCode();
883            if (!isset($this->arrStyleBullet[$bulletStyleHashCode])) {
884                $this->arrStyleBullet[$bulletStyleHashCode]['oStyle'] = $paragraph->getBulletStyle();
885                $this->arrStyleBullet[$bulletStyleHashCode]['level'] = '';
886            }
887            if (false === strpos($this->arrStyleBullet[$bulletStyleHashCode]['level'], ';' . $paragraph->getAlignment()->getLevel())) {
888                $this->arrStyleBullet[$bulletStyleHashCode]['level'] .= ';' . $paragraph->getAlignment()->getLevel();
889                $this->arrStyleBullet[$bulletStyleHashCode]['oAlign_' . $paragraph->getAlignment()->getLevel()] = $paragraph->getAlignment();
890            }
891
892            $richtexts = $paragraph->getRichTextElements();
893            $richtextId = 0;
894            foreach ($richtexts as $richtext) {
895                ++$richtextId;
896                // Not a line break
897                if ($richtext instanceof Run) {
898                    // Style des font text
899                    if (!isset($this->arrStyleTextFont[$richtext->getHashCode()])) {
900                        $this->arrStyleTextFont[$richtext->getHashCode()] = $richtext;
901                    }
902                }
903            }
904        }
905    }

964    public function writeTableStyle(XMLWriter $objWriter, Table $shape): void
965    {

1016                    }

1018                } else {
1019                    $lineStyle = 'none';
1020                    $lineWidth = Text::numberFormat($cellBorders->getBottom()->getLineWidth() / 1.75, 2);

1027                    // TOP

1043                    }

1045                    // LEFT

1047                    $lineWidth = Text::numberFormat($cellBorders->getLeft()->getLineWidth() / 1.75, 2);
1048                    $lineColor = $cellBorders->getLeft()->getColor()->getRGB();
1049                    switch ($cellBorders->getLeft()->getLineStyle()) {
1050                        case Border::LINE_SINGLE:
1051                            $lineStyle = 'solid';
1052                    }
1053                    $objWriter->writeAttribute('fo:border-left', $lineWidth . 'pt ' . $lineStyle . ' #' . $lineColor);
1054                }
1055                // >style:paragraph-properties
1056                $objWriter->endElement();

1069                }
1070            }
1071        }
1072    }
